1
00:00:00,625 --> 00:00:03,208
[2 hours ago]

2
00:00:03,208 --> 00:00:04,958
Yes, sir, it's me.

3
00:00:04,958 --> 00:00:06,125
I have an appointment right now.

4
00:00:06,125 --> 00:00:07,542
Hey, Eun Hwan.

5
00:00:07,542 --> 00:00:09,917
Seo Ah told you already, right?

6
00:00:09,917 --> 00:00:10,793
From whom?

7
00:00:10,793 --> 00:00:11,958
Park Seo Ah!

8
00:00:11,958 --> 00:00:13,375
She just decided to sign a contract with us.

9
00:00:13,375 --> 00:00:15,125
You didn't heard about it?

10
00:00:15,125 --> 00:00:17,418
No. Never heard of it.

11
00:00:17,418 --> 00:00:18,625
Really?

12
00:00:18,625 --> 00:00:21,583
Anyway, she might join the drama too.

13
00:00:21,583 --> 00:00:22,875
You should know that in advance.

14
00:00:22,875 --> 00:00:24,125
You mean...

15
00:00:24,125 --> 00:00:25,875
Yeah, 'Destined MELO'

16
00:00:25,875 --> 00:00:27,667
The articles will be published in a few days.

17
00:00:27,667 --> 00:00:30,500
So, let's meet up all together in the office sometime soon.

18
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:32,700
Alright.

19
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:35,325
I got it.

20
00:00:41,167 --> 00:00:43,283
See you today.

21
00:00:53,667 --> 00:00:55,458
You said you're busy today.

22
00:00:55,458 --> 00:00:57,378
But seems like you already had an appointment.

23
00:00:59,208 --> 00:01:01,158
Seems like you did too.

24
00:01:02,583 --> 00:01:05,250
By the looks of it, you're on a date too.

25
00:01:05,250 --> 00:01:07,042
Then, we'd better be going.

26
00:01:07,042 --> 00:01:08,875
Come on.

27
00:01:08,875 --> 00:01:11,750
They look super cute right now. Let's not bug them.

28
00:01:11,750 --> 00:01:13,742
Then, see you later.

29
00:01:39,375 --> 00:01:41,083
[Our Love Triangle]

30
00:01:41,083 --> 00:01:44,283
[EP05. My Crush's Ex]

31
00:01:49,208 --> 00:01:50,583
Why you didn't tell me in advance?

32
00:01:50,583 --> 00:01:52,458
I was about to.

33
00:01:52,458 --> 00:01:54,917
But you bailed on me right then,
saying you had something to do.

34
00:01:54,917 --> 00:01:57,375
And I couldn't get a hold of you.

35
00:01:57,375 --> 00:01:58,750
So,

36
00:01:58,750 --> 00:02:00,708
are you really going to join this project?

37
00:02:00,708 --> 00:02:01,750
Yeah.

38
00:02:01,750 --> 00:02:03,167
I want to try.

39
00:02:03,167 --> 00:02:04,992
It's a huge opportunity for me.

40
00:02:07,375 --> 00:02:09,075
You're not doing this...

41
00:02:09,667 --> 00:02:12,075
because of Hae Rin, right?

42
00:02:17,167 --> 00:02:19,527
[Encouragement Award: Awarded for outstanding
performance at the 92nd Youth Theater Festival]

43
00:02:23,833 --> 00:02:24,875
Guys!

44
00:02:24,875 --> 00:02:26,208
At this theater festival, I won--

45
00:02:26,208 --> 00:02:27,625
Seo Ah!

46
00:02:27,625 --> 00:02:30,908
Hae Rin got the grand prize at the contest!

47
00:02:33,708 --> 00:02:35,583
Really? That's really good for her.

48
00:02:35,583 --> 00:02:37,167
Congratulations!

49
00:02:37,167 --> 00:02:39,208
Thank you.

50
00:02:39,208 --> 00:02:41,625
Hae Rin, you are literally good at everything.

51
00:02:41,625 --> 00:02:43,917
You even told me that you didn't have enough time to prepare for this.

52
00:02:43,917 --> 00:02:45,583
That's what I'm saying.

53
00:02:45,583 --> 00:02:47,875
Sometimes she even makes me feel ashamed of myself.

54
00:02:47,875 --> 00:02:49,125
What?

55
00:02:49,125 --> 00:02:50,667
Why all of a sudden?

56
00:02:50,667 --> 00:02:53,375
I was the one who was supposed to get
the recommendation letter from the principal.

57
00:02:53,375 --> 00:02:55,000
You were supposed to.

58
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,792
But the rule says only one student per department gets that.

59
00:02:57,792 --> 00:03:00,792
So why can't I be that 'one student'?
Why does it have to be Hae Rin?

60
00:03:00,792 --> 00:03:02,833
She even switched her major recently.

61
00:03:02,833 --> 00:03:05,875
That's why she needs it more than you do.

62
00:03:05,875 --> 00:03:08,208
She's been struggling a lot lately after her injury.

63
00:03:08,208 --> 00:03:11,908
So, how about you let this one go for your friend, Seo Ah?

64
00:03:18,292 --> 00:03:20,250
It's not like that.

65
00:03:20,250 --> 00:03:22,000
You also know

66
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:25,417
that I've been working on something like this little by little.

67
00:03:25,417 --> 00:03:26,333
Okay, then.

68
00:03:26,333 --> 00:03:28,283
It's a relief to hear that.

69
00:03:29,875 --> 00:03:31,575
Congrats, anyway.

70
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:45,000
So, that urgent thing

71
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,950
was a date with Seo Ah?

72
00:03:48,667 --> 00:03:50,042
And then, what?

73
00:03:50,042 --> 00:03:52,333
"Seems like you already had an appointment today."

74
00:03:52,333 --> 00:03:55,033
Who's responsible for all of this?!

75
00:04:14,917 --> 00:04:17,658
How much did I drink last night?

76
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:24,566
Good morning, you slept well Hae Rin?

77
00:04:29,208 --> 00:04:30,950
What is this?

78
00:04:31,917 --> 00:04:33,658
How is this?

79
00:04:47,542 --> 00:04:48,958
I'm sorry.

80
00:04:48,958 --> 00:04:50,950
I'm so sorry.

81
00:04:54,208 --> 00:04:56,042
What?

82
00:04:56,042 --> 00:04:58,117
Cha Eun Hwan's over there.

83
00:05:00,708 --> 00:05:03,250
You jerk!

84
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:05,708
You still like her that much?

85
00:05:05,708 --> 00:05:06,750
What?!

86
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:10,208
I said you still like her that much?

87
00:05:10,208 --> 00:05:13,667
Then why did you kiss me?

88
00:05:13,667 --> 00:05:16,908
And why did you sleep with me!?

89
00:05:18,083 --> 00:05:20,000
You're such a jerk!

90
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,917
I'm seriously going to kick your ass right now.

91
00:05:22,917 --> 00:05:25,117
Come on, I will show you what I got.

92
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:33,042
Oh my. I'm such a stupid idiot.

93
00:05:33,042 --> 00:05:36,408
Why do I always end up like this after drinking?

94
00:05:49,084 --> 00:05:50,458
You just woke up?

95
00:05:50,458 --> 00:05:51,625
Yea... yeah!

96
00:05:51,625 --> 00:05:53,533
You woke up so early?

97
00:05:57,208 --> 00:05:58,625
Min Joo.

98
00:05:58,625 --> 00:06:00,833
When did you come back home last night?

99
00:06:00,833 --> 00:06:04,083
Around 3 am, I guess. We had a
student council night out last night.

100
00:06:04,083 --> 00:06:05,542
Ah, really?

101
00:06:05,542 --> 00:06:08,376
- So, you didn't come in my room, right?
- No.

102
00:06:08,376 --> 00:06:11,583
I thought you were sleeping,
so I went to sleep too straight away.

103
00:06:11,583 --> 00:06:13,375
Why?

104
00:06:13,375 --> 00:06:15,542
Thank you, thank you so much Min Joo!

105
00:06:15,542 --> 00:06:17,875
You really really did a good job.

106
00:06:17,875 --> 00:06:19,750
What did I do?

107
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:21,458
Nothing, nothing!

108
00:06:21,458 --> 00:06:23,708
Then I'm going to take a shower first!

109
00:06:23,708 --> 00:06:26,325
Unni, you dropped this.

110
00:06:36,707 --> 00:06:39,821
I should've grabbed a bite before I left.

111
00:06:39,821 --> 00:06:41,792
I've got heartburn now.

112
00:06:41,792 --> 00:06:45,708
I was planning to hit the library right after class.
Got a GE course exam tomorrow.

113
00:06:45,708 --> 00:06:47,750
We should grab something to eat after class then.

114
00:06:47,750 --> 00:06:49,200
Noona!

115
00:06:53,125 --> 00:06:54,375
What perfect timing.

116
00:06:54,375 --> 00:06:56,625
Did you get home well yesterday?

117
00:06:56,625 --> 00:06:58,625
Yeah, sure!

118
00:06:58,625 --> 00:07:00,617
I got home safely.

119
00:07:04,958 --> 00:07:05,668
Wow!

120
00:07:05,668 --> 00:07:06,917
Congrats, Seo Ah!

121
00:07:06,917 --> 00:07:07,668
What a hit!

122
00:07:07,668 --> 00:07:09,250
Is Seo Ah also a cast in this project?

123
00:07:09,250 --> 00:07:11,075
Congratulations!

124
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,333
Unni,

125
00:07:13,333 --> 00:07:15,867
I think you need to check this out.

126
00:07:22,208 --> 00:07:24,625
[Exclusive: SNS goddess Park Seo Ah
debuts as actress in Destined MELO]

127
00:07:24,625 --> 00:07:27,208
[Park Seo Ah a popular influencer with about
1.03 million followers casted in Destined MELO]

128
00:07:27,208 --> 00:07:28,917
Park Seo Ah is stunningly beautiful.

129
00:07:28,917 --> 00:07:30,750
Never miss a moment of Seo Ah Unni on screen.

130
00:07:30,750 --> 00:07:33,117
The production company really did an amazing job.

131
00:07:36,375 --> 00:07:38,117
I like you.

132
00:07:39,375 --> 00:07:40,908
What did you say?

133
00:07:41,583 --> 00:07:43,450
I'm saying I like you.

134
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,283
So, would you be my girlfriend?

135
00:07:48,208 --> 00:07:49,630
Yeah.

136
00:07:55,958 --> 00:07:57,125
I am so done already.

137
00:07:57,125 --> 00:07:59,533
Why should I have to care about Seo Ah right now?

138
00:08:09,292 --> 00:08:11,028
[Cha Eun Hwan]

139
00:08:16,667 --> 00:08:17,792
Hello?

140
00:08:17,792 --> 00:08:20,125
I'm in front of your house.
Come out for a second.

141
00:08:20,125 --> 00:08:22,125
In front of my house?

142
00:08:22,125 --> 00:08:23,500
I'm at the university right now.

143
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:24,667
I'll wait.

144
00:08:24,667 --> 00:08:26,583
It'll take just 30 minutes.

145
00:08:26,583 --> 00:08:28,116
Don't be late.

146
00:08:31,208 --> 00:08:33,500
Seemed like they're at odds with each other.

147
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:35,667
I'm worried about Hae Rin.

148
00:08:35,667 --> 00:08:38,000
You're really worried about her that much?

149
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:40,167
Then you are not worried about her?

150
00:08:40,167 --> 00:08:42,875
It's her very first drama.
She's probably under huge pressure.

151
00:08:42,875 --> 00:08:45,658
The thing about Eun Hwan and even Seo Ah.

152
00:08:46,292 --> 00:08:48,500
There are too many things going on around her right now.

153
00:08:48,500 --> 00:08:50,500
Then you tell her

154
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:52,542
that she'd better reconsider doing it.

155
00:08:52,542 --> 00:08:53,583
Who knows?

156
00:08:53,583 --> 00:08:56,708
Then, maybe I can get that chance.

157
00:08:56,708 --> 00:08:59,792
Hey, what are you saying?

158
00:08:59,792 --> 00:09:00,917
To put it bluntly,

159
00:09:00,917 --> 00:09:02,292
that's good for you too.

160
00:09:02,292 --> 00:09:03,667
What do you mean?

161
00:09:03,667 --> 00:09:06,042
Can you see her acting with Eun Hwan?

162
00:09:06,042 --> 00:09:07,825
You don't even want to imagine that, do you?

163
00:09:24,833 --> 00:09:26,867
You saw the article, right?

164
00:09:27,458 --> 00:09:29,583
How could I not?

165
00:09:29,583 --> 00:09:31,417
You already knew it, right?

166
00:09:31,417 --> 00:09:33,625
That's why you were with her that day.

167
00:09:33,625 --> 00:09:37,250
Or? Did you really think I was on a date with her?

168
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:40,500
Are you jealous of me right now?

169
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:41,528
Are you out of your mind?

170
00:09:41,528 --> 00:09:43,583
Why would I be jealous of you?

171
00:09:43,583 --> 00:09:45,625
Why not? You can be a little jealous.

172
00:09:45,625 --> 00:09:47,575
Actually, I was kinda jealous of you.

173
00:09:48,875 --> 00:09:51,158
Especially when I saw you with him.

174
00:10:01,542 --> 00:10:04,200
How can you not buckle up by yourself?

175
00:10:33,500 --> 00:10:35,200
[Our Love Triangle]
